<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Abyride Driver Application Received</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
       background: linear-gradient(135deg,#293751 0%, #47B2E4  100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
       background: linear-gradient(135deg,#293751 0%, #47B2E4  100%);
      color: #293751;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%; left: -50%;
      width: 200%; height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
    }
    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .header img {
      max-width:200px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      height:100px;
    }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    h2 {
      color: #293751;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    h3 {
      color: #293751;
      margin: 25px 0 15px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .status-badge {
      background: #E3F2FD;
      color: #293751;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border: 1px solid #BBDEFB;
    }
    .contract-details-grid, .info-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .detail-card, .info-item {
      background: #F5FAFF;
      border: 1px solid #E1F5FE;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .detail-card strong, .info-item strong {
      display: block;
      color: #293751;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .detail-card span, .info-item span {
      color: #47B2E4;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .signature-note {
      background: #E1F5FE;
      border-left: 5px solid #47B2E4;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #F5FAFF;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #E1F5FE;
    }
    .footer h3 {
      color: #293751;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #47B2E4;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .footer p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .section-title {
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .section-title::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 50px;
      height: 3px;
      background: #47B2E4;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="https://aspirebridgerwanda.org/abyride-logo.png" alt="Abyride Logo" />
      <h1>üöó Abyride Application Received</h1>
      <p>Thank you for applying to join our platform</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-section">
        <h2>Application Submitted Successfully</h2>
        <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>We've received your application and all submitted documents.</p>
        <p>Our recruitment team is currently reviewing your information and will reach out to you shortly.</p>
        <span class="status-badge">Status: Under Review</span>
      </div>

      <div class="contract-header">
        <h3>‚è≥ What to Expect Next</h3>
        <div class="contract-details-grid">
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Application Date</strong>
            <span>{{applicationDate}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Status</strong>
            <span>Pending Review</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Follow-Up Time</strong>
            <span>Within 3‚Äì5 Business Days</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Support Contact</strong>
            <span>abyridellc@gmail.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="client-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">üë§ Your Information Summary</h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Full Name</strong>
            <span>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Date of Birth</strong>
            <span>{{dateOfBirth}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Phone Number</strong>
            <span>{{phoneNumber}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Email Address</strong>
            <span>{{email}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Nationality</strong>
            <span>{{nationality}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>License ID</strong>
            <span>{{licenseId}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vehicle-section">
        <h3 class="section-title">üöô Vehicle Info </h3>
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>VIN</strong>
            <span>{{vinNumber}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Make & Model</strong>
            <span>{{make}} {{model}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Year</strong>
            <span>{{year}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <strong>Plate Number</strong>
            <span>{{plateNumber}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signature-note">
        <p>üïí Please be patient as our team processes your application. We'll be in touch shortly. Thank you for choosing Abyride!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <h3>üí¨ Need Help?</h3>
      <a href="mailto:abyridellc@gmail.com">Contact our support team any time.</a>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">
        Thanks for trusting Abyride LLC<br>
        <em>Your journey with us begins here üöò</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>